类 ClassType

  • java.lang.Object
    • cn.ficos.Compiler.Gadgets.Type.Type

  • public class ClassType
extends Type
    Type for user defined class. It stores all class information, including all class variable, class functions Remember to call ".equals(Type rhs)" to compare types
